<h1>Chrome Extension</h1>
<h2>ALPHA</h2>

<p>To download and use the extension:</p>
<ol>
  <li>
    Download the chrome extension <a href='/downloads/schedule-liberator-extension.tar.gz'>here</a>
  </li>
  <li>
    Extract the Schedule Liberator extension folder
  </li>
  <li>
    Follow the <b>Load the extension</b> instructions from <a href='http://developer.chrome.com/extensions/getstarted.html'>Google's documentation</a> to install the extension
  </li>
  <li>Use the instructions below to find your teams printable schedule</li>
  <li>Click the "Download" button</li>
</ol>

<p>To find your teams printable schedule page:</p>
<ol>
  <li>Visit the leagues home page</li>
  <li>Click on the team in question</li>
  <li>Click the SCHEDULE link under TEAM MENU</li>
  <li>Click PRINT THIS PAGE</li>
  <li>ex - http://www.pointstreak.com/players/print/players-team-schedule.html?teamid=385368&seasonid=9162</li>
</ol>
